                don't want to request privileged scopes that require Google verification.</p>
            <p class="mb-0"><strong>Important limitation:</strong> Messages sent through send-only accounts cannot be
                tracked by EmailEngine. The Gmail API modifies the Message-ID header when sending emails, and without
                read permissions, EmailEngine cannot resolve the new Message-ID assigned by Gmail. This means delivery
                status and bounce notifications may not be accurately associated with the sent message.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
